      "date": "2013-12-28 18:23:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nWhat is the performance impact of this change ? Are there extra RPCs generated due to opening files or reading the proc values? It might make sense to cache the results in a static variable for the same path prefix in llapi_search_fsname() and other expensive functions here, so they can return the results directly from userspace.",
